snippet.title: Yuppie Psycho - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
First Job Survival Horror: "Yuppie Psycho"

From the studio behind "The Count Lucanor" and the composer of "VA-11 HALL-A" arrives a new, terrifying adventure from inside a great evil corporation in an alternate 1990's. Meet your new, demented co-workers, complete tasks while running away from inkthirsty printer-monsters, and solve the most macabre of puzzles to discover the secrets buried deep within Sintracorp.
